        "type": "text",
        "content": "CUSTOM KEY ASSIGNMENT"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Custom keys may be assigned for non-standard keyboards that"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "return readable scancodes back the the PC's BIOS.  For example,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "some 3270 based keyboards, which have over 120 keys, have many"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "keys that return scancodes that do not get interpreted as"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "legitimate keycodes."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Custom key definition takes place in three parts:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "- Defining which key to customize"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "- Assigning a label to that key"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "- Assigning the SPF/PC value to that key"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
